  "title": "Staff Nurse/ Senior Staff Nurse (Anaesthesia)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Provide pre and post-operative nursing care.</li><li>Monitor and assess patient during surgical procedures.</li><li>Coordinate and collaborate with multi-disciplinary caregivers in providing safe efficient patient care.</li><li>Perform check and prepare operating room readily for procedure.</li><li>Assess patient preoperatively and complete patient safety check prior to procedure.</li><li>Check availability of supplies and anaesthetist  drugs.</li><li>Assist the anaesthetist with anaesthetic procedures.</li><li>Coordinate with surgeon or anaesthetist  to ensure smooth running of surgery list.</li><li>Perform anesthesia nursing care under supervision of surgeon in the absence of anesthetist. </li><li>Assist in other nursing duties such as circulating and monitoring of post-operative patients.   </li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Diploma / Degree in Nursing or its equivalent</li><li>At least 1 or 2 years experience as a Anaethesia nurse in clinical setting.</li><li>Registered Nurse with Singapore Nursing Board</li><li>BCLS & AED Certified</li></ul>",
